      "id": "body.solutions_ai.p.1",
      "en": "Accelerate your AI research and development with distributed GPU clusters across multiple cloud providers. Elemento provides seamless access to GPU resources, cost optimization, and framework integration for AI startups and research labs.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "solutions/ai.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.solutions_ai.p.10",
      "en": "Explore our latest insights on AI/ML infrastructure, edge computing, and cloud optimization.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "solutions/ai.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.solutions_ai.p.11",
      "en": "Discover how big data is transforming AI/ML workloads and the infrastructure needed to process massive datasets efficiently.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "solutions/ai.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.solutions_ai.p.12",
      "en": "Learn how edge computing is revolutionizing AI workloads by bringing processing closer to data sources for faster insights.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "solutions/ai.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.solutions_ai.p.13",
      "en": "Understand how virtualization optimizes AI/ML infrastructure for better resource utilization and performance.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "solutions/ai.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
